Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点事 到家再跟你说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:02.78,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3}翻译 斑马线 十八 校译 洛艾妖 时间 仓鼠 DK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多该有个女友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有骗我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有没有女朋友无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说超级跟踪狂倒是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小雪 窗户被打碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 小偷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}她潜入了我家 由乃在整理房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是我打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈去准备晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏挑这种日子来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你回来啦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么你回来了 你在做什么啊由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让妈妈认可我们之间的关系 做了一番努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}三双筷子哦~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 你快点出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去她俩真的要碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅还点着火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样子还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你在房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅啊… 我忘记关上火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是的 这多危险呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉 下次我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 由乃今天过来不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从日记得知妈妈今天会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 自己整理房间了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会做啦
