Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪和妈妈好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才怎么好像听到女孩的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是你幻听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你听 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 她到底有多大力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么顶着柜门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么呀 我只是靠在门上而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按世间常识来说 这个动作叫“顶着”哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你该不会是把女生带回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\3c&HBEC3B9&\c&H607350&\pos(537,85)\frx22\fry8\frz355.323}小雪在和妈妈说话。
